metadata.name: Owner of lives
metadata.description: We have been told since childhood that our life is in our hands. But the harsh reality shows that the lives of many people can be in the hands of unworthy and bloodthirsty dictators. He who takes the lives of innocent people will forever be doomed to severe torment. Original: Fabriano A3 pastel paper - 29*42, dry pastel, pastel pencils Derwent, Faber Castell.
